00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Allows users to register and
gain access to the social network.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
The user enters their username
and contact email address.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:14.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
A secure password is defined
and confirmed in the form.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:20.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
After filling in the details, the user
clicks the "Register" button.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:25.000 line:80% position:20% align:start
Successful registration. The user
now has full access to the platform.